The paper uses convex optimization techniques to solve the problem, which is a common technique in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with the problem of sparse structure recovery, which is a common problem in the field of artificial intelligence, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely sub-category. The paper deals with time series data, which is a common problem in the field of statistics, so cs.ST (Statistics) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also deals with the problem of latent variables, which is a common problem in the field of signal processing and information theory, so cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also likely sub-categories.
